(881, 1979, '卡巴卡 CABACA', '一群台灣CC音樂人:林強,朱頭皮,拷秋勤,張睿銓,Monbaza,MoShang.邀請馬來西亞,菲律賓,韓國,香港,日本的CC音樂人.相互支援,碰撞出無限音樂能量,成就了這個CABACA!曲風相異,理想相同,體驗音樂自由新世界!\r\n\r\n本專輯採[創用CC授權],依循條款規範可自由轉為mp3,wma,或任何形式,任意分享,散播,編輯,重混.可加上人聲蟲鳴鳥叫,可放給小朋友跳早操,歐巴桑跳土風舞,只要是非商業使用通通OK!\r\n\r\n嘻嘻哈哈做音樂,嘻嘻哈哈玩音樂,嘻嘻哈哈用音樂,就在這張!\r\n\r\nCABACA is a bold collaboration spanning across borders, languages, and music genres; it brings together artists in the Asia Pacific for the creation of new sounds to be shared worldwide.\r\n\r\nConceived in Rio in 2006 and initiated in Dubrovnik in 2007, the collaboration picked up speed after the "CC Asia Mega Mix" concert in Taipei in early 2008. The project continued to evolve through countless late night e-mails and remixes that finally gave birth to this album. Surprisingly, many of the artists taking part in CABACA have yet to meet in person even now!\r\n\r\nThe artists own this album together, and they are giving you and everyone the freedom and rights to share, remix, and share again tracks from this album.', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0, 1, 7, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:22:54', '2015-02-16 15:46:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
